OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,FTrials of the Army's troubled Ajax
OL,7,Farmoured vehicle are set to continue
OL,8,Fafter dozens of soldiers became sick
OL,9,Fduring tests in November, a defence
OL,10,Fminister has said.
OL,12,FIn a written statement published on
OL,13,FTuesday, Luke Pollard said the
OL,14,Fprogramme will be "proceeding
OL,15,Fcautiously" after use of the vehicle
OL,16,Fwas halted last year.
OL,26,@vD@SOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
