FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,FThe decision to stop using the Ajax
OL,7,Fcame after soldiers became unwell from
OL,8,Fwhat was believed to be noise and
OL,9,Fvibration during a training exercise
OL,10,Fin November.
OL,12,FThis came weeks after Pollard said the
OL,13,F#6.3 billion programme had "left its
OL,14,Ftroubles behind", declaring the
OL,15,Fvehicle manufactured by General
OL,16,FDynamics in Merthyr Tydfil, South
OL,17,FWales, was ready to be deployed on
OL,18,Foperations.
OL,26,@uD@\OUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Pollard said an
OL,7,Finvestigation found "a combination of
OL,8,Ffactors" was likely to have caused the
OL,9,Fsymptoms reported by soldiers,
OL,10,Fincluding technical issues,
OL,11,Fvariability in training and
OL,12,Fexperience, cold exposure and air
OL,13,Fquality in the Ajax.
OL,15,FHe said all personnel who reported
OL,16,Fissues in November, during Exercise
OL,17,FTitan Storm in Hampshire, have
OL,18,Freturned to normal duties and the
OL,19,Fmajority suffered from "temporary
OL,20,Fsymptoms".
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@HO]{D@XOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,FHe said: "I have now agreed to restart
OL,7,Fthe acceptance of vehicles from
OL,8,F(manufacturer) General Dynamics.
OL,9,FHowever, I accept that the experience
OL,10,Ffor our soldiers using Ajax has not
OL,11,Fbeen good enough and that is not
OL,12,Facceptable.
OL,14,F"I have implemented strict new
OL,15,Fcontrols on the reintroduction of the
OL,16,FAjax vehicles that is focused on
OL,17,Fproviding a significantly improved
OL,18,Fuser experience.
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,F"We have been engaging extensively and
OL,7,Fdirectly with our soldiers throughout
OL,8,Fthis process ` their experiences
OL,9,Fmatter and they are shaping much of
OL,10,Fwhat we do next.
OL,12,F"As a result, we are considering a
OL,13,Fphased approach to restarting the Ajax
OL,14,Fprogramme."
OL,16,FThe first phase will include the
OL,17,Frestarting of trials with a limited
OL,18,Fnumber of vehicles and under "very
OL,19,Fcontrolled circumstances", he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@KO]zD@^OU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,FThe Ajax programme, which was
OL,7,Foriginally intended to enter service
OL,8,Fin 2017, has suffered long delays
OL,9,Fbecause noise and vibration injured
OL,10,Fsoldiers who tested the vehicles.
OL,12,F"While we are proceeding cautiously
OL,13,Fwith Ajax, we know we have more to do
OL,14,Fto rebuild confidence in the vehicle,
OL,15,Fand we do not underestimate the work
OL,16,Fstill ahead," Mr Pollard added.
OL,18,F"We aspire to deliver a vehicle into
OL,19,Fservice that is effective on the
OL,20,Fbattlefield and works for our soldiers.
OL,26,@xD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,F"We will continue to work with General
OL,7,FDynamics to proceed safely,
OL,8,Fresponsibly and transparently to
OL,9,Fdeliver an improved Ajax user
OL,10,Fexperience for our soldiers.
OL,12,F"The above commitments will be met
OL,13,Fwithin the existing programme scope
OL,14,Fand financial envelope."
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
