FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,FA spokesman for General Dynamics said:
OL,7,F"GD UK welcomes the conclusions of the
OL,8,FArmy Safety Investigation Team and the
OL,9,Fdecision by the Ministry of Defence to
OL,10,Fresume acceptance and operation of
OL,11,FAjax vehicles under a phased and
OL,12,Fcarefully controlled approach, focused
OL,13,Fon delivering a significantly improved
OL,14,Fuser experience for soldiers.
OL,16,F"The safety of soldiers is, and has
OL,17,Falways been, our highest priority. GD
OL,18,FUK has confidence in the performance
OL,19,Fand protection Ajax is designed to
OL,20,Fprovide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777424606
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,Cresume after making soldiers sick
OL,6,F"It is the world's most advanced,
OL,7,Ffully digitised, armoured fighting
OL,8,Fvehicle and ensures soldiers see and
OL,9,Funderstand the battlefield faster than
OL,10,Fany adversary.
OL,12,F"GD UK is proud to be delivering this
OL,13,Fgame-changing capability for British
OL,14,Fsoldiers, with their direct feedback
OL,15,Fenabling continuous improvements.
OL,17,F"We remain committed to working in
OL,18,Fpartnership with the Army and MoD to
OL,19,Frestore the UK's war readiness and
OL,20,Fhelp support the United Kingdom's role
OL,21,Fin Nato."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
